Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: stellar
Version: 0.2.0
Summary: stellar is a tool for creating and restoring database snapshots
Home-page: https://github.com/fastmonkeys/stellar
Author: Teemu Kokkonen, Pekka PÃ¶yry
Author-email: teemu@fastmonkeys.com, pekka@fastmonkeys.com
License: BSD
Description: Stellar - Lightning fast database snapshots for development
        =======
        
        Basic usage:
        
        ```
        > stellar init
        Please enter project name (ex. myproject): my_project
        Please enter database url (ex. postgresql://localhost:5432/): postgresql://localhost:5432/
        Please enter project database name (ex. myproject): my_project_database
        Wrote stellar.yaml
        
        > stellar snapshot base
        Snapshotting database my_project_database
        > stellar list
        base a minute ago ago
        > stellar restore base
        Restore complete.
        ```
        
